Subject: [PATCH v4 02/13] dt-bindings: memory: mediatek: Add mt8195 smi sub common
Date:   Tue, 14 Sep 2021 19:36:52 +0800
Message-ID: <20210914113703.31466-3-yong.wu@mediatek.com>
